>細個成日會用普洱送嚟食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個感覺好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncake with tea / coffe 不褸都正， 唔信試下馬拉粒糕送咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60ac428e41e7e901acecc502f8290b6769ef4fb","tid":222902,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"燒賣蝦餃流沙奶黃包馬拉糕叉燒腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa2c46456cd79a0d00c3267babc2587130c53fe","tid":222902,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"馬拉榚鍾意食邊位定中間位先？"},{"pid":"717428f0833a783eb49b6b40a8c77fded4837a99","tid":222902,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19a510f2678eeec743e40f7eb72fa9ee75abd0b7","tid":222902,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"食過沙律長春卷未"},{"pid":"b21c64d66f08eee313a8f1ac63a3ad2aebf5ac13","tid":222902,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>馬拉榚鍾意食邊位定中間位先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊位先之後再食中間</blockquote><br />\n唔係喎，係一大底榚切成一份份，有 d 人鍾意食近邊位位置，有 d 就鍾意食中間位，邊位就扁 d 但就實淨 d ，中間位就鬆 d 。"},{"pid":"427cd37fbb856a43fe732506ccd2a1d67b2349c1","tid":222902,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"古法就係囉，普通既就垃撚圾"},{"pid":"c1843766e0aa34935626c064f06f5eca3624de73","tid":222902,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"食糕點會食鋁落肚？食安中心去年5月至7月在市面抽取36種食品共309個樣本作研究，包括27個預先包裝及252個非預先包裝食物，發現市民常吃的即食海蜇、雞蛋仔、馬拉糕、蒸包、烘焙糕餅等，屬含鋁量偏高的食品。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，過去在動物測試中，曾發現鋁攝取過量會影響動物的不同發育問題，對人類來說，有可能損害腎臟、發育組織、生殖能力、甚至令男性睪丸變小等，但未有証據支持鋁攝取過量與腦退化症有因果關係，也要視乎吸入鋁的份量。"},{"pid":"cd6d7cc5b052ec261870ebd5449ba22ba8981a93","tid":222902,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>馬拉榚鍾意食邊位定中間位先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊位先之後再食中間</blockquote><br />\n唔係喎，係一大底榚切成一份份，有 d 人鍾意食近邊位位置，有 d 就鍾意食中間位，邊位就扁 d 但就實淨 d ，中間位就鬆 d 。</blockquote><br />\n喺舊式茶樓聽點心姨姨講，邊位先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58632252a7859deee996d4f17bf2349f04763089","tid":222902,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"咪撚吹奏呀<br />\n第時真係變左頂點就仆街"},{"pid":"620b0d8d56644ed0f38aa20a1380b118559063e1","tid":222902,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪撚吹奏呀<br />\n第時真係變左頂點就仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ef6790342202fcfdc1efe9370e9a54bac1d6ec","tid":222902,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T23:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪撚吹奏呀<br />\n第時真係變左頂點就仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd34e03456758e03682239f2f61f1324fc68a6a","tid":222902,"uid":86377,"